query:
SELECT se.*, s.name as subjectName, u.name as professorName 
FROM student_enrollments se 
LEFT JOIN subjects s ON se.subjectId = s.id 
LEFT JOIN users u ON se.professorId = u.id 
WHERE se.studentId = 1 
LIMIT 10;
